{"tid":354966,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[Whatsapp支付測試曝光　允許用戶互相轉帳","createTime":"2017-08-11T01:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T04:36:15.000Z","uid":84266,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b91d2ba9900ff3472efd245647a7d2c7c6afe5","tid":354966,"uid":84266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:57:53.000Z","msg":"外媒披露，在WhatsApp安卓版應用2.17.295測試版本中，出現了一項WhatsApp Payment（WhatsApp支付）的新功能。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/095729_6e799c0f4e6545dd7071933c131c5b41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F095729_6e799c0f4e6545dd7071933c131c5b41.jpg&h=5d4e27d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp現擁有超過10億日活躍用戶，一向保持十分高的更新頻率，如在不到3星期前就在安卓端支持了「畫中畫」功能，現在的WhatsApp Payment無疑是一個重要的更新了。<br />\n<br />\n顧名思義，WhatsApp Payment這個功能允許用戶在應用內進行轉帳收款，而報道披露的截圖來看，此服務支持通過UPI進行銀行對銀行轉帳，用戶需要同意WhatsApp Payment的隱私條款才能使用該項服務。 <br />\n<br />\n但截至目前止，尚無更多關於WhatsApp Payment的細節，也有猜測認為WhatsApp將允許用戶在對話過程中進行轉帳。這種點對點(P2P)支付的模式與同類應用無異。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170810/mobile/bkn-20170810153649267-0810_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170810%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170810153649267-0810_00842_001.html&d=vOTBSNjuBlgphOHGkzXh6YM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=64667917\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170810/mobile/bkn-20170810153649267-0810_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9af26630183ca89ddfc561f31d04bed16a6f7f42","tid":354966,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"whatsapp可以俾錢轉錢，不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0bbb7fd7ebf2a2f29dc3beec6b4f2156026241","tid":354966,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"咁就要睇佢收唔收手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"h